OL,3,CHeating oil firms accused of
OL,4,Cprofiteering as some customers see
OL,5,Cprices double
OL,7,FThere have been more worrying warnings
OL,8,Fthat the economic impact of the War
OL,9,Fcould prompt a further jump in the
OL,10,FUK's cost of living. It's not just
OL,11,Fprices at the petrol pumps causing
OL,12,Fconcern: heating oil has also seen
OL,13,Fhuge spikes since the start of the
OL,14,FIran War. ITV News Political
OL,15,FCorrespondent Harry Horton and
OL,16,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi report
OL,18,FThere are accusations of "blatant
OL,19,Fprofiteering" as the government sends
OL,20,Fa warning to the heating oil industry.
OL,26,@zD@ZOU{D@MO]
