OL,3,CHeating oil firms accused of
OL,4,Cprofiteering as some customers see
OL,5,Cprices double
OL,7,FSome customers are facing a doubling
OL,8,Fof prices as the Iran conflict
OL,9,Funsettles energy markets. Yet, the
OL,10,Festimated 1.5 million UK households
OL,11,Fthat rely on this fuel have no
OL,12,Fprotection from the energy price cap.
OL,14,FOne anxious customer, Eira Featley in
OL,15,Frural Suffolk, told ITV News last time
OL,16,Fshe filled her tank it was about #300
OL,17,F- and today's price - #707.94.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
