OL,3,CHeating oil firms accused of
OL,4,Cprofiteering as some customers see
OL,5,Cprices double
OL,7,F"You've got to heat your house", she
OL,8,Fsays, "There's a cold spell coming up,
OL,9,Fso it's scary. What's gonna happen if
OL,10,Fthis continues?"
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning
OL,17,FThe Iran conflict sparked daily price
OL,18,Ffluctuations up to 10p a litre
OL,19,Faccording to the Fuel Distribution
OL,20,FAssociation.
