OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773220132
OL,3,CHeating oil firms accused of
OL,4,Cprofiteering as some customers see
OL,5,Cprices double
OL,7,FFigures seen by ITV News show examples
OL,8,Fof costs moving from 61p a litre
OL,9,Fbefore the conflict to #1.52 after.
OL,11,FThe Energy Secretary Ed Miliband has
OL,12,Fwritten to the industry, warning
OL,13,F"Government will take all action
OL,14,Fnecessary to protect households".
OL,16,FThe Former Conservative Energy
OL,17,FSecretary Claire Coutinho MP has said
OL,18,Fsome of her constituents have
OL,19,Fexperienced "blatant profiteering",
OL,20,Fadding "heating oil customers are
OL,21,Fbeing ripped off."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
