OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773220132
OL,3,CHeating oil firms accused of
OL,4,Cprofiteering as some customers see
OL,5,Cprices double
OL,7,FITV News spoke to Ken Cronin, who
OL,8,Fheads the heating oil distributors
OL,9,Ftrade association.
OL,11,FHe told us, "Fuel distributors have
OL,12,Flimited stock on their sites, so those
OL,13,Fdistributors are buying that fuel on
OL,14,Fthe day at the market prices. Thats
OL,15,Fthe reason why you have seen such a
OL,16,Fbig shift in prices increasing to the
OL,17,Fcustomer."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
